citations:
    citation-asos-jon-i:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Jon I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Jon Snow rides with wildlings (Rattleshirt, Ygritte, Longspear Ryk, Ragwyle) down the Milkwater. Encounters the Weeper and Harma Dogshead's outriders. Jon presented to Mance Rayder in his tent at the wildling camp. Styr (Magnar of Thenn), Tormund Giantsbane, Dalla (Mance's pregnant queen), Val (Dalla's sister), and Jarl are introduced. Mance reveals he was at Winterfell when King Robert visited. Jon justifies his apparent defection."
